I use the binary directly but I have a script as well.

    #!/bin/bashcd "/home/user/.local/share/Steam/SteamApps/common/Kerbal Space Program/"LC_ALL=C LD_PRELOAD="libpthread.so.0 libGL.so.1" __GL_THREADED_OPTIMIZATIONS=1 ./KSP.x86_64

I just find this more convenient than the Steam client.
